Description: 1D water level interpolation through an S4 class and several
    functions which utilize internally provided datasets and gauging data. The
    S4 class (WaterLevelDataFrame) structures the computation and visualisation
    of 1D water level information along the German federal waterways Elbe and
    Rhine. 'hyd1d' delivers 1D water level data - provided by the 'FLYS'
    database - and validated gauging data - provided by the hydrological
    database 'HyDaBa' - package-internally. For computations near real time
    gauging data are queried externally from 'PEGELONLINE'.
